questions.questionText:
In Java, what is the output of this code?
for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
System.out.println(i);
}

What is the output of this Python loop?
for i in range(3, 6):
  print(i)

What is the output of this Java code?
int i = 0;
while (i < 2) {
  System.out.println(i);
  i++;
}

What will happen in this Python code?
while False:
  print("Hello")

What is the output of this code?
int i = 0;
do {
  System.out.println(i);
  i++;
} while (i < 3);

In Java, what will happen in this do-while loop?
int i = 0;
do {
  i--;
} while (i > 0);
